Class Move.PawnPromotion

java.lang.Object
engine.forBoard.Move
engine.forBoard.Move.PawnMove
engine.forBoard.Move.PawnPromotion
Enclosing class:
Move
public static class Move.PawnPromotion extends Move.PawnMove
The PawnPromotion class represents a special move in chess. When a pawn reaches the opponent's back rank, it can be promoted to any other chess piece (queen, rook, bishop, or knight). This class extends a standard PawnMove by adding promotion information and handles the execution of the promotion move.
Author:
Aaron Ho
